    "description": "If you're a passionate Floor Manager with drive and ambition, Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates in Howrah is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates:\nGodrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates!",
